name: Wrapped Cybria
description: Cybria is a modular blockchain with AI for efficiency, transparency, and security. Designed to address the limitations by providing a scalable, secure, and efficient Layer 2 solution. CybriaChain Mainnet is an EVM-equivalent Layer 2 blockchain connected to Ethereum. CybriaChain is standardized and shared, forming a network of OP Stack chains that share a bridging protocol, governance system, and more.
